217
00:18:03,320 --> 00:18:04,680
He's extremely cunning.

218
00:18:04,680 --> 00:18:06,160
I couldn't get him to come here nicely.

219
00:18:07,320 --> 00:18:07,960
All right, all right,

220
00:18:07,960 --> 00:18:08,840
just go. Go.

221
00:18:52,120 --> 00:18:53,000
