223
00:19:27,120 --> 00:19:28,160
It's the Ensnaring Vines.

224
00:19:28,440 --> 00:19:29,760
Do you know of this poison?

225
00:19:30,440 --> 00:19:31,240
This poison

226
00:19:31,240 --> 00:19:33,120
is mainly made from wood moth larvae,

227
00:19:33,160 --> 00:19:33,920
mixed with toxic plants

228
00:19:33,920 --> 00:19:34,800
