244
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:09,760
one of our Maidens disappeared,

245
00:20:09,960 --> 00:20:11,280
and she's never heard from again.

246
00:20:12,120 --> 00:20:13,000
So, it's possible that

247
00:20:13,280 --> 00:20:14,280
the Maiden was

248
00:20:14,280 --> 00:20:15,800
linked to the Fire Moth Sect

249
00:20:15,840 --> 00:20:17,000
and shared this poison recipe.

250
00:20:17,760 --> 00:20:18,560
Impossible!

251
00:20:18,760 --> 00:20:19,440
That's Dai Si.

252
00:20:19,440 --> 00:20:21,040
She would never collude with a cult.

253
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:22,320
You're the Holy Maiden.

254
00:20:22,360 --> 00:20:23,440
You must have the antidote,

255
00:20:23,440 --> 00:20:24,200
right?

256
00:20:31,800 --> 00:20:32,440
Before I came,

257
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:34,280
I heard a bit about this from Pan Chi.

258
00:20:34,280 --> 00:20:35,480
I searched through our texts

259
00:20:35,480 --> 00:20:36,600
and made a special antidote.

260
00:20:36,600 --> 00:20:37,960
I hope it works.

261
00:20:40,800 --> 00:20:41,960
